<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10517152>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Euodynerus semiaethiopicus (Giordani Soika, 1943), paralectotypes. A, habitus in dorsal view, male. B, head in frontal view, male. C, head in frontal view, female. D, flagellum in lateral view, male. E, head in dorsal view, female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10517152/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10517158>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Male genitalia: aedeagus in ventral view, aedeagus in lateral view, digitus + volsella. A, Euodynerus gaya Selis, sp. nov. B, Euodynerus histrionicus (Gerstäcker, 1857). C, Euodynerus niloticus (de Saussure, 1855). D, Euodynerus salzi (Giordani Soika, 1952). E, Euodynerus semiaethiopicus (Giordani Soika, 1943)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10517158/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10517160>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Distribution map of Afrotropical species of Euodynerus Dalla Torre." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10517160/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

